Adahn.Backstory: This friendly slime alien had dreams of being a pod racer someday, but then he was kidnapped by a maniac seeking El Dorado, who died and left him to be burned alive. He survived that, but later a different maniac seeking El Dorado knocked him out and robbed him. Now he seeks revenge on all El Dorado parties for the rest of time.
Adahn.Name: Adahn Elriot
Inventory: El Dorado Party Murdering Space Blaster

Big.Name: Big Java
Big.Backstory: Leader of a rich family of warlords, and famed as the leader of one of the only groups of people to ever reach El Dorado.

Billiamina.Backstory: One of the most dangerous shapeshifters in the universe. She speaks to the dead and often takes their form, but the real danger is how insanely cool she is. Many trends mysteriously start and turn out to have been Billiamina's fault the whole time.
Billiamina.Name: Billiamina

Blob.Name: Blob Slave
Blob.Backstory: Cons people like there's no tomorrow. Basically has no moral code. Upon finding out that the blob could change traits, decided to grind RNG for 17 hours until he got the ones he wanted. What a god.

Chad.Backstory: Chad Gaylord Smith (born October 25, 1961) is an American musician who has been the drummer of the band Red Hot Chili Peppers since 1988. The group was inducted into the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame in 2012. Smith is also the drummer of the hard rock supergroup Chickenfoot, formed in 2008, and of the all-instrumental outfit Chad Smith's Bombastic Meatbats, formed in 2007. On his journey to El Dorado, he discovered his love for alchemy.
Chad.Name: Chad Gaylord Smith

Daddy.Name: Daddy Yankee
Daddy.Backstory: Literally what is the appeal of Nacho Cheese. We need to genocide everyone who likes that abomination of a flavor.

Dmitriyev.Backstory: The smartest bear in the universe.
Dmitriyev.Name: Dmitriyev

Ekaterini.Backstory: It may seem hard to believe, but this...creature...was once famous blogger Dildo Swaggins. She became an alcoholic vlogger obsessed with guns, to the point where she is now literally a gun with legs.
Ekaterini.Name: Ekaterini Tikitiki

Gustava.Backstory: Gustava feels like she got the short end of the shapeshifting stick. She married another invisible person and they go around stealing money.
Gustava.Name: Gustava

Ivanovich.Name: Ivanovich
Ivanovich.Backstory: The grandson of Dmitriyev. I think that probably makes him a bear?

JOG.Name: JOG MANSEN
JOG.Backstory: JOG MANSEN’s sole mission is to get every NPC to change their name to JOG to create the army of JOG to do his bidding. He has been doing pretty well for himself, creating a new wizard school named JOGwarts with his army of 1000 JOGs that knocked Hogwarts out of business.

JOGSAMPSEN.Name: JOG SAMPSEN
JOGSAMPSEN.Backstory: He once worked for HOG BRANSEN, but JOG convinced him to change sides. On the road to El Dorado, he discovered his true passion: wedding planning. The voices tell him their favorite ships and he makes them a reality.

JOGSOLO.Name: JOG SOLO
JOGSOLO.Backstory: JOG MANSEN is his loving husband. After traumatically having his mouth stolen, JOG SOLO got 16 extra mouths at El Dorado which are now all over his body.

Jacques.Backstory: Oh my god! It's Chad Gaylord Smith's long lost twin sibling!!! What a coincidence that they have showed up just now!
Jacques.Name: Jacques Fatality Theron

Kim.Name: Kim Jong Dos
Inventory: Iron Fist of the Golden Ruler
Kim.Backstory: The Mexican stepbrother of dictator Kim Jong Un.

Leandra.Backstory: A child that enjoys cosplaying as Death and saying random creepy things. She was the computer girl for ISIS, but then she went to JOGwarts and became a wizard.
Leandra.Name: Leandra Erk

Leopoldo.Backstory: Grew up in an inner city neighborhood. Dislikes cottage cheese. Definitely not secretly a lizard person.
Leopoldo.Name: Leopoldo Pedro Raven

Liam.Name: Liam Payne
Liam.Backstory: Liam is known as the dude who made the most transcendent album of all time. He tries to keep a low profile nowadays, mostly because he is mobbed by teenage girls whenever he goes outside.

Luis.Backstory: He and Daddy Yankee were ultimately unable to get over their Dorito-related differences. The ensuing war has killed millions of people.
Luis.Name: Luis Fonsi

Magahet.Name: Magahet
Magahet.Backstory: MAGA for Republican. Het for heterosexual. They were once a nurse before they found Augustus, the love of their life, who proceeded to get them a 10-year prison sentence. Now they are a plastic surgeon, who still gets idiot customers despite being blind.

Morty.Name: Morty P. Sherman III
Morty.Backstory: A hero who resurrected Rick Sanchez from the form of a pickle. He has realized that he no longer needs friends, just vegetables.

Otis.Backstory: A 70 year old fat man from Minnesota who is in love with Morty. Morty refuses to marry him and Otis is very upset about it.
Otis.Name: Otis Phil

Pinkbeard.Backstory: Pinkbeard changes her gender every day. She has invented 74 new genders in order to change her gender more.
Pinkbeard.Name: Pinkbeard the Vegetarian

Savanna.Backstory: Despite streaming on Twitch for 10 years, they have never garnered more than 5 viewers. And one of them is their stalker so it's really 4.
Savanna.Name: Savanna Gregg

Svetlana.Backstory: Some jackass stole their trusty Bagpipe. Now they seek revenge.
Svetlana.Name: Svetlana Datura Acey

Topham.Backstory: He was looking for a female train as all the trains on the Island of Sodor are male, then he was transformed into an ogre and then into a human, and now he is the leader of all the trains. After this adventure, he became a member of ISIS and then joined JOG MANSEN to reach El Dorado.
Topham.Name: Topham Hatt

Vena.Backstory: A proud member of ISIS and follower of JOG MANSEN. Who knows what her mission is.
Vena.Name: Vena Wilburn

Leia.Backstory: They lost three family members in the Great Dorito War. They are now a peace activist hoping to end the conflict between the two sides.
Leia.Name: Charles
